          <p>
            I work as a freelance software engineer. I love solving business problems with reliable, well-proven
            technology.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <span class="font-bold">Past</span>
        <p>
          Most recently, I was part of a startup that scaled from its beginnings to enterprise clients in the reverse
          logistics and returns space, helping major retailers turn returns into revenue and sustainability wins.
        </p>
        <p>
